entry.title: U.S. Strikes Syrian Militias as Israel Makes Fresh Incursion Into Gaza
entry.content: The U.S. strikes were the first American response to what officials said were a number of attacks against U.S. personnel and facilities in Iraq and Syria by Iranian-backed militias.

entry.title: Manhunt for Shooting Suspect Turns Maine's Second Largest City Into Ghost Town
entry.content: Even the 7-Eleven closed amid shelter-in-place orders. The sole named suspect is still at large.
